<h3 class="heading"><span class="type">Paragraph</span></h3>
<p>We know that <span class="process-math">\(a=\dfdx{v}{t}=\dfdxn{y}{t}{2}=-9.8\)</span> so</p>
<div class="displaymath process-math" data-contains-math-knowls="">
\begin{align*}
\dx{v}\amp=-9.8\dx{t}\\
\int\dx{v}\amp=\int-9.8\dx{t}\\
v+c_1\amp=-9.8t+c_2\\
v\amp=-9.8t+(\underbrace{c_2+c_1}_{= c})
\end{align*}
</div>
<span class="incontext"><a href="section-3.html#p-33" class="internal">in-context</a></span>
